<plot>Filmmaker Lyn Gerner introduces us to the passionate international team who have come from around the tropical Atlantic to the Bahamas to research the lionfish: the first Indo-Pacific species to become invasive in the Atlantic. The team fights against time and tide to understand the invader and control the invasion.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?619185</url></doc>
